William C. Griffiths 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman of the Board, President & Chief Executive Officer at QUANEX BUILDING PRODUCTS, William C. Griffiths  made $3,717,466 in total compensation.  Of this total $813,654 was received as a salary, $1,192,359 was received as a bonus, $575,904 was received in stock options, $1,103,567 was awarded as stock and $31,982 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


