William C. Griffiths

Age : 65Public asset : 3,532,367 USDLinked companies :  Quanex Building Products Corporation 





Summary 



Mr. William C. Griffiths is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Quanex Building Products Corp. Mr. Griffiths was previously employed as Managing Director & Director by Sealine International Ltd., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by CEI Liquidation Estates, President-Fluid Systems Division by SPX Corp., President-Fluid Systems Division by United Dominion Industries Ltd., Vice President by AMB Property Corp., and President & Chief Executive Officer by Champion Enterprises Holdings LLC.He also served on the board at Wolverine Tube, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of London.



