William C. Griffiths



Mr. William C. Griffiths is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Quanex Building Products Corp.
Mr. Griffiths was previously employed as a Managing Director & Director by Sealine International Ltd., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by CEI Liquidation Estates, President-Fluid Systems Division by SPX Corp., President-Fluid Systems Division by United Dominion Industries Ltd., President & Chief Executive Officer by Champion Enterprises Holdings LLC, and Vice President by AMB Property Corp. He also served on the board at Wolverine Tube, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of London.



